Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Voting for equal rights
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043www5
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 21 Nov 1982
Women vote against Republicans following loss of Equal Rights Act. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.